readable.content: A black dachshund sniffs another dog wearing a striped shirt . A dog wearing a striped sweater touches noses with another dog . A white dog wearing a zepra print shirt is nose to nose with a black dog wearing a pink collar . A white dog with a sweater on and a black and brown dog touching noses . Two dogs meeting nose to nose .
